{"id":426314,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/01/426314/","date":"2016-01-22T20:18:34Z","modified":"2016-01-22T20:19:03Z","title":"【立存此照】爱国小粉红“复杂像”","content":"<blockquote><p>转自奇闻录19日消息：1月19日下午，黄安手动清空了自己新浪微博的<a href=\"http://weibo.com/u/2489313225?topnav=1&amp;wvr=6&amp;topsug=1&amp;is_all=1\">所有言论</a>，至此其2014年至今的所有微博均被清除殆尽，他清除微博的动机尚不得知。他在微博举报周子瑜一事似乎就要结束，然而不少“爱国小粉红”的墙外讨伐战还在继续，该事件之后，一些“爱国小粉红”与台湾网友发生了争执、对骂，后来演变成所谓的“互发表情包大战”，更多小粉红甚至“翻墙增援”参与骂战。当然，与各种洗版的表情包相比，更有趣的还是不少小粉红令人脑洞大开的评论。</p></blockquote>\n<p>较为常见的表情包  已经泛滥FB相关页面</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-426318\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/902421526000626548-1.jpg\" alt=\"902421526000626548\" width=\"440\" height=\"727\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/902421526000626548-1.jpg 719w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/902421526000626548-1-182x300.jpg 182w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/902421526000626548-1-620x1024.jpg 620w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></p>\n<p>为中国防火墙辩护的小粉红</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426319\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/8d245a62gw1f042wbhtv6j20f00qoafc.jpg\" alt=\"8d245a62gw1f042wbhtv6j20f00qoafc\" width=\"440\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/8d245a62gw1f042wbhtv6j20f00qoafc.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/8d245a62gw1f042wbhtv6j20f00qoafc-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426320\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/8d245a62gw1f042wf5txfj20f00qotdz.jpg\" alt=\"8d245a62gw1f042wf5txfj20f00qotdz\" width=\"440\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/8d245a62gw1f042wf5txfj20f00qotdz.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/8d245a62gw1f042wf5txfj20f00qotdz-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426321\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/8d245a62gw1f042whl2ngj20f00qo7a4.jpg\" alt=\"8d245a62gw1f042whl2ngj20f00qo7a4\" width=\"440\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/8d245a62gw1f042whl2ngj20f00qo7a4.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/8d245a62gw1f042whl2ngj20f00qo7a4-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426322\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/8d245a62gw1f042wi4w7aj20f00qowif.jpg\" alt=\"8d245a62gw1f042wi4w7aj20f00qowif\" width=\"440\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/8d245a62gw1f042wi4w7aj20f00qowif.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/8d245a62gw1f042wi4w7aj20f00qowif-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-426323\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZPdL60WEAAXPDu.jpg\" alt=\"CZPdL60WEAAXPDu\" width=\"440\" height=\"365\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZPdL60WEAAXPDu.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZPdL60WEAAXPDu-300x249.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-426326\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZVXVszUkAElnxv.jpg\" alt=\"CZVXVszUkAElnxv\" width=\"500\" height=\"253\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZVXVszUkAElnxv.jpg 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZVXVszUkAElnxv-300x152.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>施展“我作为你爸”钓鱼计的小粉红</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-426325\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZSs2C4WYAEyEgR.jpg\" alt=\"CZSs2C4WYAEyEgR\" width=\"450\" height=\"482\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZSs2C4WYAEyEgR.jpg 513w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZSs2C4WYAEyEgR-280x300.jpg 280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>没有看懂@阑夕微博言论的小粉红</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426330\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZUMrmMUkAEflRq.jpg\" alt=\"CZUMrmMUkAEflRq\" width=\"440\" height=\"744\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZUMrmMUkAEflRq.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZUMrmMUkAEflRq-177x300.jpg 177w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426328\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZUMrmNU8AAReu3.jpg\" alt=\"CZUMrmNU8AAReu3\" width=\"440\" height=\"753\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZUMrmNU8AAReu3.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZUMrmNU8AAReu3-175x300.jpg 175w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426329\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZUMrjJVAAAW-6X-1.jpg\" alt=\"CZUMrjJVAAAW-6X\" width=\"439\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZUMrjJVAAAW-6X-1.jpg 439w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZUMrjJVAAAW-6X-1-232x300.jpg 232w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 439px) 100vw, 439px\" /></p>\n<p>在蔡英文页面怒刷八荣八耻的小粉红</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-426334\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZKc1w2UsAADCTO.jpg\" alt=\"CZKc1w2UsAADCTO\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZKc1w2UsAADCTO.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZKc1w2UsAADCTO-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZKc1w2UsAADCTO-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>感觉“八荣八耻”作用不大的小粉红</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426331\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZS_tKcWkAAxnlp.jpg\" alt=\"CZS_tKcWkAAxnlp\" width=\"438\" height=\"453\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZS_tKcWkAAxnlp.jpg 438w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZS_tKcWkAAxnlp-290x300.jpg 290w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 438px) 100vw, 438px\" /></p>\n<p>没有历史认知的小粉红</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426332\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/7Qz1G.jpg\" alt=\"7Qz1G\" width=\"451\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/7Qz1G.jpg 451w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/7Qz1G-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 451px) 100vw, 451px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-426333\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZPemUEWwAAtogo.png\" alt=\"CZPemUEWwAAtogo\" width=\"550\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZPemUEWwAAtogo.png 599w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZPemUEWwAAtogo-300x248.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>不按照套路出牌的小粉红</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-426324\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZTV1w0WIAAv43I.jpg\" alt=\"CZTV1w0WIAAv43I\" width=\"450\" height=\"586\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZTV1w0WIAAv43I.jpg 496w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/CZTV1w0WIAAv43I-230x300.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>然而在人民日报评论文章中 爱国小粉红却是全然不同的另外形象：</p>\n<blockquote><p>转自人民日报22日<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/01/%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e6%97%a5%e6%8a%a5-%e8%af%84%e5%b8%9d%e5%90%a7%e5%87%ba%e5%be%81fb%ef%bc%9a90%e5%90%8e-%e7%9b%b8%e4%bf%a1%e4%bd%a0%e4%bb%ac/\" target=\"_blank\">评论</a>：在这场网络较量中，与中国内地这些90后的青少年们相比，一些持“台独”观点的人显得笨拙、无知、狭隘和自大。通过这次“网络大战”，双方综合素养高下立判。</p>\n<p>更让人惊叹的是，这些自发组织的以90后为主的一群人（甚至包括一些00后），竟然有详细的分工、严明的纪律，在facebook上只打台独而不伤台胞感情。可以看出，中国新一代90后的青少年们已经开始登上历史舞台了，他们自信地迈着阔步，天马行空地自由挥洒，他们充满阳光和自信的表现，让人眼前一亮。</p>\n<p>这些大家自我的约束，更充分说明，将大量来自天南海北的、彼此互不相识的网友凝聚在一起的，绝非戾气，而是大家对于台湾最朴素的情感，以及对“统一”最真诚的希望。</p></blockquote>\n<p>例如会发美食图片</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426300\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/233932DA316E567F20659CF61DF813A3.png\" alt=\"233932DA316E567F20659CF61DF813A3\" width=\"288\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/233932DA316E567F20659CF61DF813A3.png 288w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/233932DA316E567F20659CF61DF813A3-150x300.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 288px) 100vw, 288px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>例如会发诗句<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426305\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/C110D7E8D62021000FDE634DDF1447A0.png\" alt=\"C110D7E8D62021000FDE634DDF1447A0\" width=\"359\" height=\"399\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/C110D7E8D62021000FDE634DDF1447A0.png 359w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/C110D7E8D62021000FDE634DDF1447A0-270x300.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 359px) 100vw, 359px\" /></p>\n<p>例如会”有理有据“地反驳台湾媒体</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426309\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/EC768B6BA60D1EF0A5F7F859A5A83883.png\" alt=\"EC768B6BA60D1EF0A5F7F859A5A83883\" width=\"446\" height=\"432\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/EC768B6BA60D1EF0A5F7F859A5A83883.png 446w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/EC768B6BA60D1EF0A5F7F859A5A83883-300x291.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 446px) 100vw, 446px\" /></p>\n<p>那爱国小粉红的形象，到底是怎样的呢？还是如胡锡进的“复杂中国论”，爱国小粉红的样貌也是复杂的，不过有一点，他们几乎都是翻墙而来的，他们几乎都在灌水式地表达着自己的意见。</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[30060,8639,18904,11967,30044,30039,14076,8795]}